**Anything else relevant?**
I was looking for this issue and found an article on angular.io, which says that [Destructured variables are not supported in AoT](https://angular.io/guide/aot-compiler#destructured-variable-not-supported).  
I am not sure if this also applies for my example, but if it does, it should probably show an error instead of resulting in a wrong bundle.
I already created this [issue in angular/angular-cli](https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/issues/14302) and was told that I should open it here, as it is a compiler issue.

